---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Hero from "../components/Hero.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Board" description="Learn about the Lago Bello HOA Board of Directors, how elections work, and how to get involved.">
  <Hero title="Board of Directors" />

  <!-- About the Board -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16" aria-label="About the board">
    <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl mb-6">Your Board</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-slate-light leading-relaxed mb-4">
      The Lago Bello HOA is governed by a Board of Directors elected by and from the homeowners
      of our community. The Board is responsible for managing the Association's common areas,
      enforcing the CC&Rs, setting the annual budget, and making decisions that protect and
      improve our neighborhood.
    </p>
    <p class="text-lg text-slate-light leading-relaxed">
      Board members are your neighbors — volunteers who dedicate their time to keeping
      Lago Bello a great place to live. Their authority and responsibilities are defined
      in the community
      <a href="/documents/exhibit-c-bylaws/" class="text-primary hover:text-primary-light font-semibold">Bylaws</a>.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- How Elections Work -->
  <section class="bg-white border-y border-cream-dark" aria-label="Elections">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl mb-6">How Elections Work</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-cream rounded-xl p-6 border border-cream-dark">
          <h3 class="font-heading text-lg text-primary-dark mb-3">Annual Meeting</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-light leading-relaxed">
            The Board of Directors is elected at the Annual Meeting of the Association. Every
            homeowner in good standing is entitled to attend and vote. Meeting notices are sent
            to all members in advance.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-cream rounded-xl p-6 border border-cream-dark">
          <h3 class="font-heading text-lg text-primary-dark mb-3">Who Can Serve</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-light leading-relaxed">
            Any homeowner who is a member of the Association in good standing may be nominated
            to serve on the Board. Directors serve terms as defined in the Bylaws and may be
            re-elected.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-cream rounded-xl p-6 border border-cream-dark">
          <h3 class="font-heading text-lg text-primary-dark mb-3">Voting</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-light leading-relaxed">
            Each lot is entitled to one vote. Votes may be cast in person at the Annual Meeting
            or by proxy. A quorum of members must be present or represented for the election
            to proceed.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-cream rounded-xl p-6 border border-cream-dark">
          <h3 class="font-heading text-lg text-primary-dark mb-3">Officers</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-light leading-relaxed">
            Once elected, the Board appoints officers from among its members — typically a
            President, Vice President, Secretary, and Treasurer — to handle the day-to-day
            business of the Association.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Get Involved -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16" aria-label="Get involved">
    <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl mb-6">Get Involved</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-slate-light leading-relaxed mb-8">
      A strong community depends on the participation of its residents. Whether you have
      five minutes or five hours a month, there are meaningful ways to contribute.
    </p>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-cream-dark">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading text-lg text-primary-dark mb-2">Attend Meetings</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-light leading-relaxed">
          Come to the Annual Meeting and any special meetings called by the Board. Your voice
          and your vote shape the direction of our community.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-cream-dark">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-sage/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-sage" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 19.128a9.38 9.38 0 002.625.372 9.337 9.337 0 004.121-.952 4.125 4.125 0 00-7.533-2.493M15 19.128v-.003c0-1.113-.285-2.16-.786-3.07M15 19.128v.106A12.318 12.318 0 018.624 21c-2.331 0-4.512-.645-6.374-1.766l-.001-.109a6.375 6.375 0 0111.964-3.07M12 6.375a3.375 3.375 0 11-6.75 0 3.375 3.375 0 016.75 0zm8.25 2.25a2.625 2.625 0 11-5.25 0 2.625 2.625 0 015.25 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading text-lg text-primary-dark mb-2">Volunteer</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-light leading-relaxed">
          The ACC, lake maintenance, landscaping, and community events all benefit from resident
          volunteers. No experience needed — just a willingness to pitch in.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-cream-dark">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-lake/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-lake" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading text-lg text-primary-dark mb-2">Run for the Board</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-light leading-relaxed">
          Interested in helping guide our community? Consider running for a seat on the Board
          at the next Annual Meeting. New perspectives are always welcome.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact CTA -->
  <section class="bg-white border-y border-cream-dark" aria-label="Contact the board">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl mb-4">Questions or Ideas?</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-light leading-relaxed mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        The Board is always open to hearing from homeowners. Whether you have a question,
        a suggestion, or want to learn more about getting involved, don't hesitate to reach out.
      </p>
      <a
        href="mailto:board@lagohoa.org"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-primary text-cream font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-light transition-colors"
      >
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21.75 6.75v10.5a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25 2.25h-15a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25-2.25V6.75m19.5 0A2.25 2.25 0 0019.5 4.5h-15a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25 2.25m19.5 0v.243a2.25 2.25 0 01-1.07 1.916l-7.5 4.615a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.36 0L3.32 8.91a2.25 2.25 0 01-1.07-1.916V6.75" />
        </svg>
        Email the Board
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
